ors thesis or working on a writing in the major project for further details please go to our honors page or our writing in the major page for additional support and information about wim please click on the undergraduate academic life's wim resources page special ihum group tutoring sessions need additional support as you draft your ihum essay the hume writing center is pleased to announce group tutoring sessions a chance for you to work with your peers and with a writing tutor as you draft your essay look out for announcements in your residences and check the google docs f or the most up to date information about when and where introsem consulting during the summer the hume writing center offers online introsem consulting to help undergraduate students write compelling application essays even while they are off campus and abroad students are able to chat with a trained writing consultant in real time by connecting through google chat vchat and google docs during the academic year we offer students the same high quality consultation in person peer consultants if you are currently a peer consultant click here for more information including timecard submission information becoming a peer writing consultant all stanford undergraduates are invited to apply to become hume writing center peer writing consultants the application process is competitive every year in february 15 20 new tutors are hired from a pool of 50 60 applicants during the spring quarter new consultants take a 3 credit training course pwr195 and then begin tutoring the following fall peer consultants are chosen on the strength of their written application faculty recommendations and an interview click here for some position details updated 1 17 2012 voices on writing hwc programs writing in the major introductory seminars honors writing and boot camp digital media consulting pwr stanford university 590 escondido mall stanford ca 94305 3069 650 723 2631 contact us terms of use copyright complaints site b